## Customization

- Edit skills in `skills/` to customize Claude's behavior
- Modify agents in `agents/` to adjust subagent capabilities
- Update hooks in `hooks/hooks.json` to change automation rules
- Adjust design tokens in `config/design-system.json`
- Edit `.mcp.json` to add, remove, or reconfigure MCP servers

## Updating

When a new version of Enterprise Superpowers is released, re-run `init` to regenerate with the latest integrations:

```bash
npx enterprise-superpowers init {{companySlug}}
```

To add a single integration without regenerating everything:

```bash
npx enterprise-superpowers add <integration-name>
```

